- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper is about developing an algorithm for parsing sentences. 
- cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) is a possible category as the paper uses a neural network framework. 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is a less likely category, but still possible as pointer networks have been used in computer vision tasks as well.
